MESSAGE.value: Added open track from URL menu item and associated methods.
Added open track from URL menu item.
Got rid of Tools, fixed some accelerators.
Better error handling for remote BAM file problems.
Fixed typo in tools menu variable name.
Disable load track from URL until genome is set.
Squish mode for BED, improvements to squish mode for generic intervals, redrawing when display mode changes.
Fixed block merging algorithm and tweaked drawing at different resolutions.
Some more tweaks to arrow drawing: don't draw if there is not enough room.
Fixed fasta formatting to deal with blank lines.
Intervals must be one base larger to account for the fact that Intervals are non-inclusive of the last position.
Made data types immutable, moved into data.types package.
